t bowls","caption":"A Gumtree Kids sensory station set up under the trees in the gardens at Historic Rivermill","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"400"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"6a26d444db7bd9527908ce3b","authoredDate":"2026-06-09","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/93bd9bfe2e7fc2b767360a312b445b15.jpeg?rect=0%2C150%2C1600%2C900&w=1600&h=900&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjZhMjZiYWE3ZDFlYWEyNjExMzYxZWI4MyIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"1600","height":"900","altText":"Young girl laughing behind an outdoor sensory tray filled with seeds, wooden tools and coconut bowls","caption":"A Gumtree Kids sensory station set up under the trees in the gardens at Historic Rivermill","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"400"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"6a26d444db7bd9527908ce3b","authoredDate":"2026-06-09","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/93bd9bfe2e7fc2b767360a312b445b15.jpeg?rect=0%2C150%2C1600%2C900&w=800&h=450&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjZhMjZiYWE3ZDFlYWEyNjExMzYxZWI4MyIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"800","height":"450","altText":"Young girl laughing behind an outdoor sensory tray filled with seeds, wooden tools and coconut bowls","caption":"A Gumtree Kids sensory station set up under the trees in the gardens at Historic Rivermill","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"400"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"6a26d444db7bd9527908ce3b","authoredDate":"2026-06-09","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/93bd9bfe2e7fc2b767360a312b445b15.jpeg?rect=0%2C150%2C1600%2C900&w=280&h=158&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjZhMjZiYWE3ZDFlYWEyNjExMzYxZWI4MyIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"280","height":"158","altText":"Young girl laughing behind an outdoor sensory tray filled with seeds, wooden tools and coconut bowls","caption":"A Gumtree Kids sensory station set up under the trees in the gardens at Historic Rivermill","photographer":"","copyright":"","sequenceNumber":"400"}],"openTimes":[],"productComments":[{"marketVariantId":"English / Global","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ENGLISH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"English","commentText":"Historic Rivermill on the banks of the Coomera River in the Gold Coast Hinterland hosts Messy Play — Animal Friends, a sensory play session for young children presented by Gumtree Kids. The session pairs hands-on messy play stations with close encounters with the animals on the property, set within the gardens and paddocks beside the river. The programme is designed for families with toddlers and pre-school aged children, who explore textures, colours, and natural materials in an open-air setting."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"O histórico Rivermill às margens do rio Coomera, no interior da Gold Coast, oferece o Messy Play — Animal Friends, uma sessão de brincadeiras sensoriais para crianças pequenas, apresentada pela Gumtree Kids. A sessão combina estações de brincadeiras sensoriais com encontros próximos com os animais da propriedade, em meio aos jardins e pastos à beira do rio. O programa é voltado para famílias com crianças pequenas e em idade pré-escolar, que exploram texturas, cores e materiais naturais em um ambiente ao ar livre."},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"골드코스트 내륙 지역 쿠메라 강변에 위치한 유서 깊은 리버밀에서 검트리 키즈(Gumtree Kids)가 주최하는 어린이를 위한 감각 놀이 프로그램인 '메시 플레이 - 동물 친구들(Messy Play - Animal Friends)'이 열립니다. 이 프로그램은 강변 정원과 목초지에서 다양한 질감과 색깔 자연 소재를 탐색하며 오감을 자극하는 체험 활동으로 구성되어 있습니다. 특히 유아 및 미취학 아동을 둔 가족을 위해 설계된 이 프로그램은 탁 트인 야외 공간에서 아이들이 직접 만지고 느끼며 놀 수 있는 기회를 제공합니다."},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Lo storico Rivermill, sulle rive del fiume Coomera nell'entroterra della Gold Coast, ospita Messy Play — Animal Friends, una sessione di gioco sensoriale per bambini piccoli presentata da Gumtree Kids. La sessione combina postazioni di gioco interattive con incontri ravvicinati con gli animali della proprietà, all'interno dei giardini e dei recinti lungo il fiume. Il programma è pensato per famiglie con bambini piccoli e in età prescolare, che esplorano consistenze, colori e materiali naturali in un ambiente all'aria aperta."},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"El histórico molino Rivermill, a orillas del río Coomera en el interior de la Costa Dorada, presenta «Juegos sensoriales: Amigos de los animales», una actividad para niños pequeños organizada por Gumtree Kids. La sesión combina estaciones de juego prácticas y creativas con encuentros cercanos con los animales de la propiedad, en los jardines y prados junto al río. El programa está diseñado para familias con niños pequeños y preescolares, quienes explorarán texturas, colores y materiales naturales al aire libre."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Le moulin historique Rivermill, situé sur les rives de la rivière Coomera dans l'arrière-pays de la Gold Coast, accueille « Messy Play — Animal Friends », une séance d'éveil sensoriel pour les jeunes enfants présentée par Gumtree Kids. Cette séance combine des ateliers de manipulation et d'exploration sensorielle avec des rencontres privilégiées avec les animaux de la propriété, au cœur des jardins et des enclos bordant la rivière. Le programme est conçu pour les familles avec des tout-petits et des enfants d'âge préscolaire, qui peuvent ainsi découvrir des textures, des couleurs et des matériaux naturels en plein air."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Die historische Rivermill am Ufer des Coomera River im Hinterland der Gold Coast bietet „Messy Play – Animal Friends“ an, ein Sinneserlebnis für Kleinkinder, präsentiert von Gumtree Kids. In diesem Programm können Kinder an verschiedenen Stationen kreativ mit verschiedenen Materialien experimentieren und gleichzeitig die Tiere des Anwesens in den Gärten und Weiden am Fluss hautnah erleben. Das Angebot richtet sich an Familien mit Kleinkindern und Vorschulkindern, die in der Natur Texturen, Farben und Naturmaterialien entdecken möchten."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"ゴールドコースト内陸部のクーメラ川沿いにある歴史的なリバーミルでは、ガムツリーキッズ主催の幼児向け感覚遊びセッション「メッシープレイ ― アニマルフレンズ」が開催されます。このセッションでは、川沿いの庭園や牧草地に設置された、実際に触れて遊べる泥遊びコーナーと、敷地内の動物たちとの触れ合いが組み合わされています。幼児や未就学児のご家族向けに企画されたこのプログラムは、屋外で様々な質感、色、自然素材を探求することを目的としています。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"位于黄金海岸腹地库梅拉河畔的历史悠久的河畔磨坊（Rivermill）举办“趣味涂鸦——动物朋友”感官游戏活动，由Gumtree Kids呈现，专为幼儿设计。活动将动手涂鸦游戏与近距离接触磨坊内的动物相结合，地点设在河畔的花园和牧场中。该项目专为有幼儿和学龄前儿童的家庭设计，旨在让孩子们在户外环境中探索不同的质地、颜色和天然材料。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"位於黃金海岸腹地庫梅拉河畔的歷史悠久的河畔磨坊（Rivermill）舉辦「趣味塗鴉－動物朋友」感官遊戲活動，由Gumtree Kids呈現，專為幼兒設計。活動將動手塗鴉遊戲與近距離接觸磨坊內的動物結合，地點設在河畔的花園和牧場。該計畫專為有幼兒和學齡前兒童的家庭設計，旨在讓孩子們在戶外環境中探索不同的質地、顏色和天然材料。"},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Rivermill yang bersejarah di tepi Sungai Coomera di pedalaman Gold Coast menyelenggarakan Messy Play — Animal Friends, sesi bermain sensorik untuk anak-anak kecil yang dipersembahkan oleh Gumtree Kids. Sesi ini menggabungkan stasiun bermain kotor yang interaktif dengan interaksi langsung dengan hewan-hewan di properti tersebut, yang terletak di dalam taman dan padang rumput di tepi sungai. Program ini dirancang untuk keluarga dengan balita dan anak-anak usia prasekolah, yang mengeksplorasi tekstur, warna, dan bahan-bahan alami di lingkungan terbuka."}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Historic Rivermill","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"950 Beaudesert Nerang Road","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Mount Nathan","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4211","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.9760432","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.2507233","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"ALLTICKETS","ratesTypeDescription":"All tickets","priceFrom":"20","priceTo":"30","free":"","rateComment":""}],"deals":[],"jobVacancies":[],"weather":"","menuUrl":"","winelistUrl":"","doesServeMeal":"","openingTime":{"openingTimeType":"","seasonalPeriods":[],"openingTimeComment":"","exceptions":{"exceptionPeriod":"","periods":[]}},"productProximity":[],"productWidget":[],"services":[],"verticalClassifications":[{"productTypeId":"EVTCLASS","productTypeDescription":"Classes, Lessons, Workshops and Talks"}],"pageURL":"/au/en/things-to-do/events/p-6a26baa7d1eaa2611361eb83-messy-play-at-historic-rivermill","classificationLaye